## XCBGetFDFromDisplay

(xcb\_util.c %P%)

`int XCBGetFDFromDisplay(const char *name, int *screenp, XCBAuthInfoHost *host)`

Calls:

- [XCBParseDisplay](http://xcb.freedesktop.org/wiki/)
